hopobject.body: A pension scheme owl pharmacy california Well, but the negotiations we had were extremely minor and keep in mind.  There was two different things.  Number one is the economy was growing and the deficit was going down.  Before we ever signed the balanced budget amendment, 90% of the deficit was gone, because of economic growth and what the Congress voted for in our economic plan in ’93.  So it was– we didn’t give away the store and they didn’t ask us to give away the store.
